title: FIFA President Sepp Blatter will not resign despite major sponsors calling for him to go immediately
text: 3 Oct 2015 FIFA President Sepp Blatter will not resign despite major sponsors Coca-Cola, Visa, Budweiser and McDonald's calling for him to go immediately.The four sponsors issued statements saying Blatter should quit after Swiss criminal proceedings were opened against him last week. Â»
